---
title: Loaded Beef & Chorizo Jacket Potatoes with Cheddar Cheese & Avocado Salad
description: Get a load of this: crisp and golden jacket potatoes, topped with a moreish beef mince and chorizo topping - which comes together
in the pan with a good glug of tomato paste and our trusty Aussie spice blend. Serve with a simple salad to balance out the richness,
and top it all off with mandatory shredded Cheddar, plus a sprinkling of sesame seeds for a nutty depth of flavour.
